code: @Override protected AbstractStringProcessor newProcessor(String field, boolean ignoreMissing, String targetField) {     return new TrimProcessor(randomAlphaOfLength(10), field, ignoreMissing, targetField). }

@Override protected String modifyInput(String input) {     String updatedFieldValue = "".     updatedFieldValue = addWhitespaces(updatedFieldValue).     updatedFieldValue += input.     updatedFieldValue = addWhitespaces(updatedFieldValue).     return updatedFieldValue. }
@Override protected String expectedResult(String input) {     return input.trim(). }
private static String addWhitespaces(String input) {     int prefixLength = randomIntBetween(0, 10).     for (int i = 0. i < prefixLength. i++) {         input += ' '.     }     return input. }
